urdu transliteration text:
Hum Rahain Yeh Azadari Rahay Shama se Shama Jale
xxx
@HujjatELC

Apni Naslon Lo Sikhate Raho, Matam ka hunar,Seena dar Seena Kare, Bus Yeh Azadari Safar,Jaise Halaat Bhi Ho, rasm yeh Jaari Rahe.
xxxx
@HujjatELC

Laakh Badle yeh Zamane Ki ravish aur MausamEk Pal Bhi Na Ruke Ashk e Aza Aur Matam,Matam e Sheh Ka Junoon Zehen Par taari rahe.
xxxx
@HujjatELC

Tum agar Zakir e Shabbir (as) Ho Yeh Yaad Rahe,Chahe Is gham ke Liye sar Bhi kate Ghar Bhi Jale Hurmat e Farsh e Aza, Jaan Se Pyari Rahe,
xxxx
@HujjatELC

Yeh Sabile yuhni Aabad rahe Ahle Aza, Aur Ghar Ghar Pe Nazar Aaye Alam Ghazi (as) Ka,ye alam Ooncha Rahe Yeh Alamdari Rahe,
xxxx
@HujjatELC

Duniya Walon Ki Na Parvah haan na kuch baat Karo, Manaati Bediyan Sajjad ke gham Me Pehno,Raunake Farsh e Aza Girya O Zaari Rahe
xxxx
@HujjatELC

Maao Behno Ko Hai Paigum mera sirf yehi,Aapne Bacchon Julooson Se Nahi Roko Kabhi,Yeh Shahadat Hai Sharaf, Yeh Sharaf Jaari Rahe
xxxx
@HujjatELC
